      "text": "# IFS Technical Documentation: Demo\nAuto-extracted from docs.ifs.com/techdocs/ for PR review validation.\n\n## Projection Model Guidelines\nSource: [Projection Model Guidelines](https://docs.ifs.com/techdocs/26r1/dev/040_development/022_marble_models/050_projection/index.html)\n\nA projection defines the data model and integration APIs in IFS Cloud. Always specify the correct categories. EntitySet definitions expose entities.\n\n---\n\n## Projections\nSource: [Projections](https://docs.ifs.com/techdocs/26r1/dev/040_development/022_marble_models/050_projection/index.html#projections)\n\nProjections are declarative endpoints. Always check that the projection name matches naming conventions.\n\n---",
